'''Sector [[Constable/Legends|Constable]]''' was a [[Police rank|title]] used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] in the time of the [[Mandalorian Wars]]. The [[Police officer/Legends|individual]] was in charge of all [[Law enforcement agency/Legends|law enforcement]] affairs for an entire [[Sector/Legends|sector]]. In [[3964 BBY|3964]] &mdash; [[3963 BBY]], [[Taris/Legends|Taris]]' [[Ojoster sector/Legends|Sector]] Constable was [[Noana Sowrs]] until she fell to the [[Rakghoul plague/Legends|Rakghoul plague]].

